  <body>
    <% include regist.ejs %>
    <% include header.ejs %>
    <div class="jumbotron">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>欢迎访问！</h1>
        <p>班级在线交流平台，登录后可聊天，分享学习资料，发布课后感想</p>
